<!-- Node: "QuakeCon 2004" -->
<div class="body_box_header">QuakeCon 2004</div>
<div class="body_box"><small>Submitted by <a href="http://www.gamedesign.net/user/view/1804" title="View user profile.">Kingpin_Xatrix</a> on Thursday, April 8, 2004 - 12:19</small><br /><br />
This year <a href = "http://www.quakecon.org/">QuakeCon</a>'s registration will be a little different. Tournament and BYOC sign-ups, will be seperate. On April 14th at 9pm Eastern, registration will still be open. Everyone who plans to attent <b>QuakeCon</b> should sign up. As usual, all sign-ups will be on a first-come, first-serve basis.
